body:
Cyberpunk 2077 Spoilers?

Me and my friends were talking about the E3 Cyberpunk 2077 trailer and he pointed out that Keanu Reeves appears to be a hologram and not really there. Which lead us to speculate on what that could mean, and the most logical conclusion we came up with was that Keanu’s character, Johnny Silverhand, is some kind of mental projection only visible to the player. (Because in the official Cyberpunk cannon Johnny Silverhand is assumed dead, no body was found but…)

Upon reaching this conclusion I had a thought. In Cyberpunk 2077 the protagonist uses a mental projection of Keanu Reeves to reach his goals. In the musical Be More Chill the protagonist uses a mental projection of Keanu Reeves to reach his goals. Do Be More Chill and Cyberpunk take place in the same universe or is Cyberpunk 2077 some kind of AU of Be More Chill?
